SUMMARY:Natural Wine Tasting at Great Bear Vineyard
DESCRIPTION:Natural Wine Tasting at the Vineyard in Davis \n Saturday\, May 9 | 12–5pm\nReady to taste something wonderfully different? Step into the world of Black Bicycle Farm’s natural\, orange\, and wildly expressive wines at Great Bear Vineyards. \nThis guided tasting is a flavorful journey through purity\, creativity\, and the personality of the vineyard itself. Crafted from organically grown grapes with minimal intervention\, these wines let nature do the talking—and trust us\, they have a lot to say.\n What to Expect: Five distinct natural wines\, each with its own story A chance to explore orange wine\, unfiltered whites\, and playful reds Insight into the philosophy and artistry of natural winemaking A relaxed afternoon in the rustic beauty of the winery\n Featured Wines Include:\nSquiggle 2023 – Bold\, structured orange wine with citrus layers and textured depth\nOrange Tipple 2023 – Elderflower aromas with vibrant apricot\, honey\, and orange notes\nClash of the Titans 2022 – Cabernet Sauvignon & Zinfandel blend bursting with red and dark fruit\nAfter the Fire 2020 – Cabernet Sauvignon harvested during the 2020 wildfires—smoky\, spicy\, unforgettable\nCarbo Cab 2019 – Playful\, unfiltered Cabernet with Bing cherry\, candied strawberry\, and lively carbonic energy\n Whether you’re a seasoned natural wine fan or simply curious to try something new\, this tasting promises to be eye-opening\, delicious\, and full of character.\n Come sip outside the lines.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/natural-wine-tasting-at-great-bear-vineyard/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Highway128PressTrip_GreatBearVineyards_2024_MaxWhittaker_12-Copy-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
