SUMMARY:Cupcake and Bubbles at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Cupcake & Bubbles at the Vineyard in Davis \n Sunday\, May 10 | 12–3pm\nCelebrate Mom with a sparkling afternoon of sweetness\, sunshine\, and vineyard charm. \nTreat the special women in your life to a relaxing experience featuring your choice of a glass of handcrafted sparkling wine or a refreshing mimosa\, perfectly paired with a delicious cupcake. It’s the sweetest way to slow down\, savor the moment\, and celebrate together.\n Ticket Includes: Glass of Sparkling Wine or Mimosa Cupcake\nSurrounded by sunlit vines and springtime blooms\, raise a glass to the women who do it all—mothers\, grandmothers\, daughters\, and dear friends. \n Join us as we toast to love\, gratitude\, and the joy of celebrating Mom in style.\n Please Note: No outside food allowed on Mother’s Day.Cheese\, salami\, crackers\, and snacks will also be available for purchase.\n Make this Mother’s Day extra sweet at the vineyard!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/cupcake-and-bubbles-at-great-bear-vineyards/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Highway128PressTrip_GreatBearVineyards_2024_MaxWhittaker_12-Copy-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
