SUMMARY:Pick Your Own Bouquet at Park Winters
DESCRIPTION:This seasonal farm hospitality experience\, offered most Saturdays and Sundays\, includes everything you need to create a beautiful farm-grown bouquet. Wander through the flower rows and enjoy a peaceful countryside outing while our team guides you on how to clip and gather your blooms. \nYour freshly picked flowers will be wrapped in a moisture-soaked paper wrap to keep them fresh until they are placed in a vase at home. \nWhile we will accommodate walk-in guests when availability allows\, reservations are recommended. On the booking page\, simply select the number of bouquets you would like to create. \nAs this experience is guided by nature\, flower varieties change throughout the season. If field conditions do not meet expectations\, a full refund is available upon request.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/pick-your-own-bouquet-at-park-winters/2026-05-16/
LOCATION:Park Winters\, Park Winters\, 27850 County Road 26 Winters\, CA 95694
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/ES0A7883-1-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
